<app-navbar title="AI 助手" left-arrow="{{false}}" />

<view class="page-body page-body--with-tabbar">
  <view class="summary-banner">
    <view class="icon-title-row">
      <t-icon name="info-circle" size="48rpx" class="ui-icon ui-icon--primary" />
      <view class="summary-title">社区 AI 助手</view>
    </view>
    <view class="summary-desc">后续可以接公告解读、财务问答、流程引导和投票建议，这里先把推荐问题和入口统一到同一套列表交互。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section card info-card">
    <view class="icon-title-row">
      <t-icon name="view-list" size="40rpx" class="ui-icon ui-icon--primary" />
      <view class="section-title">你可以这样问</view>
    </view>
    <app-list
      list="{{suggestions}}"
      loading="{{loading}}"
      showLoading="{{false}}"
      isLoadMore="{{isLoadMore}}"
      finished="{{finished}}"
      emptyDescription="暂无推荐问题"
      bind:refresh="onListRefresh"
      bind:loadMore="onListLoadMore"
    >
      <t-cell-group>
        <t-cell wx:for="{{suggestions}}" wx:key="*this" title="{{item}}" note="待接入" />
      </t-cell-group>
    </app-list>
  </view>

  <view class="section page-note">
    当前仅保留页面结构和入口，等后续接入模型能力后，这里可以直接扩展为完整的问答页。
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <button class="primary-button">开始对话</button>
  </view>
</view>

<app-tabbar value="assistant" />
